To run CAMB:
see jet:cosmosims/CAMB/
params.ini contains all parameters you need including sigma8 and omegas... prefix for files is set and matter power spectrum is output.
>camb params.ini
if you modify the cosmology and need a specific sigma8,  run the code, go back inside and modify scalar_amp(1)  by multiplying 
scalar_amp(1)  =  scalar_amp(1)  *(desired_sigma/output_sigma)^2 
units are P(k)=h-3Mpc^3 with k=h/Mpc
